---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <div
    class="bg-stone-50 text-stone-600 antialiased selection:bg-orange-200 selection:text-orange-900"
  >
    <header
      class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center pt-20 overflow-hidden"
    >
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <video
          src="/video-header.mp4"
          autoplay
          loop
          muted
          playsinline
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          aria-hidden="true"></video>
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-r from-stone-900/40 via-stone-900/20 to-transparent"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-stone-50 via-transparent to-transparent"
        >
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 w-full grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center"
      >
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <h1
            class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-semibold text-white tracking-tight leading-[1.1] text-shadow-sm"
          >
            <span data-i18n="hero.titleBefore">Le soleil de la</span>{" "}
            <span
              class="text-yellow italic font-serif"
              data-i18n="hero.titleHighlight">Réunion</span
            >{" "}
            <span data-i18n="hero.titleAfter">dans votre assiette.</span>
          </h1>

          <p
            class="text-lg text-stone-100 max-w-lg leading-relaxed font-light"
            data-i18n="hero.subtitle"
          >
            Voyagez à 10 000 km sans quitter le sud de la France. Une cuisine
            artisanale, épicée et généreuse, préparée avec amour et tradition.
          </p>

          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 pt-4">
            <a
              href="#menu"
              class="group flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-blue hover:bg-orange text-yellow px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-all shadow-xl shadow-blue-500/20"
            >
              <iconify-icon
                icon="solar:chef-hat-linear"
                width="20"
                stroke-width="1.5"></iconify-icon>
              <span data-i18n="hero.ctaMenu">Voir la Carte</span>
            </a>
            <a
              href="#book"
              class="group flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-yellow hover:bg-orange text-blue px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-all shadow-xl shadow-yellow-500/20"
            >
              <iconify-icon
                icon="solar:calendar-linear"
                width="20"
                stroke-width="1.5"></iconify-icon>
              <span data-i18n="hero.ctaBook">Réserver une table</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
  </div>

  <section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-32 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div
      class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mr-20 -mt-20 w-96 h-96 bg-yellow rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-50"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1 relative group">
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-stone-900 rounded-2xl rotate-2 group-hover:rotate-1 transition-transform opacity-10"
        >
        </div>
        <img
          src="/photo-13.jpeg"
          alt="Épices et cuisine"
          data-i18n-alt="about.imageAlt"
          class="relative rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full h-[500px] object-cover -rotate-1 group-hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="order-1 md:order-2 space-y-6">
        <div
          class="flex items-center gap-2 text-blue font-medium text-sm tracking-wide uppercase"
        >
          <span class="w-8 h-px bg-blue"></span>
          <span data-i18n="about.label">Notre Histoire</span>
        </div>
        <h2
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-stone-900 tracking-tight"
          data-i18n="about.title"
        >
          Des racines volcaniques au cœur du sud de la France.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="about.paragraph1">
          Née a Saint-Denis, notre Cheffe Elisette a emporté dans ses valises
          les secrets de sa grand-mère. Ô Phil d'Elo n'est pas juste un
          restaurant, c'est un pont entre deux cultures.
        </p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
          <span data-i18n="about.paragraph2Before"
            >Nous cuisinons comme à la maison : le
          </span>
          <span class="text-blue font-medium" data-i18n="about.curcuma"
            >curcuma</span
          >
          <span data-i18n="about.paragraph2After">
            (safran péi), le combava et la vanille bourbon rythment nos
            préparations. Une cuisine de partage, chaleureuse et sans artifice.</span
          >
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 pt-4">
          <div>
            <iconify-icon
              icon="solar:heart-angle-linear"
              class="text-blue mb-2"
              width="32"
              stroke-width="1.5"></iconify-icon>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-stone-900" data-i18n="about.homemade">
              Fait Maison
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div>
            <iconify-icon
              icon="solar:bottle-linear"
              class="text-blue mb-2"
              width="32"
              stroke-width="1.5"></iconify-icon>
            <h4
              class="font-semibold text-stone-900"
              data-i18n="about.rhumArrange"
            >
              Rhum Arrangé
            </h4>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="menu" class="py-24 bg-white border-y border-stone-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <h2
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-stone-900 tracking-tight mb-4 text-blue"
          data-i18n="menu.title"
        >
          La Carte des Saveurs
        </h2>
        <p class="text-stone-500" data-i18n="menu.subtitle">
          Une sélection de nos plats signatures, évoluant au gré des saisons et
          des arrivages du marché.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="mt-8 text-center flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4"
      >
        <a
          href="/menu.pdf"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-900 hover:text-blue font-medium transition-colors border-b border-stone-300 pb-1 hover:border-orange-600"
        >
          <span data-i18n="menu.downloadFull">Télécharger le menu complet</span>
          <iconify-icon
            icon="solar:file-download-linear"
            width="18"
            stroke-width="1.5"></iconify-icon>
        </a>
        <a
          href="#book"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-orange transition-colors"
        >
          <iconify-icon
            icon="solar:calendar-linear"
            width="18"
            stroke-width="1.5"></iconify-icon>
          <span data-i18n="hero.ctaBook">Réserver une table</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="gallery" class="py-24 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-12 gap-6"
      >
        <div>
          <h2
            class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-blue tracking-tight"
            data-i18n="gallery.title"
          >
            Immersion Tropicale
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-500 mt-2" data-i18n="gallery.subtitle">
            Une ambiance décontractée et chaleureuse.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 h-[600px] md:h-[500px]">
        <div
          class="col-span-2 row-span-2 relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden group"
        >
          <img
            src="/photo-1.jpeg"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
            alt="Intérieur du restaurant"
            data-i18n-alt="gallery.altInterior"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden group">
          <img
            src="/photo-10.jpeg"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
            alt="Cocktail"
            data-i18n-alt="gallery.altCocktail"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden group">
          <img
            src="/photo-14.jpeg"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
            alt="Dessert"
            data-i18n-alt="gallery.altDessert"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden group">
          <img
            src="/photo-4.jpeg"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
            alt="Dessert"
            data-i18n-alt="gallery.altDessert"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden group">
          <img
            src="/photo-6.jpeg"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
            alt="Dessert"
            data-i18n-alt="gallery.altDessert"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="infos" class="relative text-stone-300 py-24 overflow-hidden">
    <div
      class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px from-transparent via-stone-700 to-transparent"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-yellow rounded-full blur-[100px]"
    >
    </div>

    <div
      class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 relative z-10"
    >
      <div class="space-y-10">
        <div>
          <h2
            class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-blue tracking-tight mb-2"
            data-i18n="info.title"
          >
            Infos Pratiques
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-400" data-i18n="info.subtitle">
            Retrouvez-nous au Cap d'Agde.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div
            class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-stone-800 transition-colors"
          >
            <div class="p-2 bg-blue rounded-lg text-yellow">
              <iconify-icon
                icon="solar:map-point-linear"
                width="24"
                stroke-width="1.5"></iconify-icon>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h4
                class="text-blue font-medium mb-1"
                data-i18n="info.addressLabel"
              >
                Adresse
              </h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">
                <span data-i18n="info.addressLine1"
                  >24 QUAI DI DOMINICO LE CAP D AGDE</span
                >
                <br />
                <span data-i18n="info.addressLine2">34300 AGDE</span>
              </p>
            </div>
            <a
              href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/%C3%94+Phil+d'Elo+974/@43.2849787,3.5092657,17.32z/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0x12b13b506b487fc3:0x9c7c4ae1d07fd423!8m2!3d43.2845434!4d3.5095494!16s%2Fg%2F11fylw82d_!5m1!1e1?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDQwNS4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="shrink-0 p-2 bg-yellow text-blue rounded-lg hover:bg-orange transition-colors"
            >
              <iconify-icon
                icon="solar:point-on-map-linear"
                width="20"
                stroke-width="1.5"></iconify-icon>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div
            class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-stone-800 transition-colors"
          >
            <div class="p-2 bg-blue rounded-lg text-yellow">
              <iconify-icon
                icon="solar:clock-circle-linear"
                width="24"
                stroke-width="1.5"></iconify-icon>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4
                class="text-blue font-medium mb-1"
                data-i18n="info.hoursLabel"
              >
                Horaires
              </h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">
                <span data-i18n="info.hours"
                  >Lundi - Dimanche : 12h00 - 15h30 / 18h30 - 22h30</span
                >
                <br />
                <span data-i18n="info.closedWednesday">Mercredi : Fermé</span>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        id="book"
        class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-stone-800 shadow-2xl shadow-black/20"
      >
        <h3
          class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 tracking-tight text-blue"
          data-i18n="booking.title"
        >
          Réserver une table
        </h3>
        <p class="mb-4 text-stone-600" data-i18n="booking.subtitle">
          Contactez-nous pour une réservation :
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a
            href="tel:+33640080525"
            class="bg-blue text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-orange transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                d="M2 3a1 1 0 011-1h2.153a1 1 0 01.986.836l.74 4.435a1 1 0 01-.54 1.06l-1.548.773a11.037 11.037 0 006.105 6.105l.774-1.548a1 1 0 011.059-.54l4.435.74a1 1 0 01.836.986V17a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2C7.82 18 2 12.18 2 5V3z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            <span data-i18n="booking.call">Appeler</span>
          </a>
          <a
            href="sms:+33640080525"
            class="bg-blue text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                d="M2 5a2 2 0 012-2h7a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H9l-3 3v-3H4a2 2 0 01-2-2V5z"
              ></path>
              <path
                d="M15 7v2a4 4 0 01-4 4H9.828l-1.766 1.767c.28.149.599.233.938.233h2l3 3v-3h2a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2h-1z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            <span data-i18n="booking.sms">Envoyer un SMS</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="text-stone-500 py-8 text-sm">
    <div
      class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4"
    >
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="font-bold text-blue tracking-tight">Ô Phil d'Elo</span>
        <span class="text-stone-600">|</span>
        <span data-i18n="footer.rights">© 2026 Tous droits réservés.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
